One of the main features of the program is its ability to grab and download embedded [[Flash Video]] files from sites like [[YouTube]], [[Dailymotion]], [[Metacafe]] etc. Orbit Downloader also accelerates downloads by acting as a peer-to-peer client, utilising bandwidth of other users.
